content.rendered:
Directed by Suresh Triveni

Written by Prajwal Chandrashekar. Abbas Dalal. Hussain Dalal. Suresh Triveni

Star Vidya Balan (Maya Menon). Shefali Shah (Ruksana Mohammad). Rohini Hattangadi (Rukmini). Vidhatri Bandi (Rohini George). Manav Kaul (Anand). Iqbal Khan (Amar Malhotra). Surya Kasibhatla (Ayush Menon). Shrikant Yadav (Head Constable More). Ghanshyam Lalsa (ASI Pradeep). Gurpal Singh (Judge Gulati). Shafeen Patel (Imad Mohammad). Sharad (Salim Mohammad). Kashish Rizwan (Alia Mohammad). Junaid Khan (Rizwan). Vijay Nikam (Ramnik Bhai). Trushant Ingle (Ramnik’s Son #1). Monu Gurjar (Rafique). Uday Vir Singh Yadav (Vinodji). Mangesh Desai (SI Poddar). Sanjana Deshmukh (Tanuja). Sofiya Khan (Broker Ruby). Sahil Brown (Alam). Abbas Dalal (Javed Bhai). Ajit Kelkar (Maya’s Neighbor)

Language Hindi

Producers Debodeep Chakraborty. Bhushan Kumar. Krishan Kumar. Krishan Kumar. Vikram Malhotra. Shikhaa Sharma. Ravi Tiwari. Suresh Triveni. Karuna Vishwanath

Production Abundantia Entertainment. T-Series Films
